          "order": 2,
          "title": "ESTIMATES ARE ABOUT TIME, SO LET'S CUT TO THE CHASE",
          "summary": "Estimating tasks in software development is difficult. However, it’s still important to estimate in time rather than abstract points. Estimating in time helps provide a clearer understanding of timelines and costs for both internal and external stakeholders, as well as encouraging deeper task analysis.",
